Class Provider

    • com.firebase.authwrapper.providers.delegate.Provider

    IProvider

    public class Provider
extends java.lang.Object
implements IProvider
    the delegate is used for encapsulate methods and data which not relevant to the user. The end users will be using IProvider interface in order to interact with the concrete provider.
